      "name": "Bench-scale hemolysis validation against FDA pump experimental data",
      "description": "CFD-predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) compared against published experimental NIH measurements for the FDA generic centrifugal pump across 5 operating points. Mean relative error 8.3%; all predictions within experimental uncertainty bounds. RH < 1 satisfied at worst-case operating point."
    },
