    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 requirements. Validation evidence demonstrates NIH predictions within combined uncertainty bounds across all COU operating points. UQ performed via Monte Carlo sampling characterizes output uncertainty under input variability. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. RH < 1 criterion satisfied at all evaluated operating points.",
